column2: select enrollment.SystemStudentID , enrollment.GradeLevel as EnrollmentGrade , enrollment.SchoolYear4Digit , enrollment.isActiveEnrollment , count (parent.EventDate) as Parent_Score from Enrollment enrollment left join ParentEngagement parent on enrollment.SystemStudentID = parent.StudentID and enrollment.SchoolYear4Digit = parent.SchoolYear4Digit group by enrollment.SystemStudentID , enrollment.GradeLevel , enrollment.SchoolYear4Digit , enrollment.isActiveEnrollment
